<chapter id="using-kslovar">
<title>Using &kslovar;</title>

<!-- This chapter should tell the user how to use your app. You should use as
many sections (Chapter, Sect1, Sect3, etc...) as is necessary to fully document
your application. -->

<para>
When starting &kslovar;, it will update its languages file. You can disable it in Settings->Configure KSlovar->Behaviour. To start, you
should create a dictionary by clicking File->New Dictionary or opening an existing one.

